CREATE DATABASE
1-İnstall Heidisql.
2-Creating the localhost database.
3-Right click create new databese 
4-Right click again and create new table
5-Write the data
6-Edit data types
7-Make the first part special.
8- Right click the ID and make it private, then save as auto increment.

MYSQLi CODES
1-mysqli_connect(“servername”,”admin”,”password”,”database_name”); => Establishes a connection with the database.
2-mysqli_connect_error(); => Prints if there is an error.
3-mysqli_set_charset(“utf8”)=> It is used to prevent the Turkish character problem.
4-mysqli_fetch_assoc();=>Data was received.
5-mysqli_query()=> run the querty.
